Name: F_SYSTEM
Code2: Principal Arterial – Other Freeways and Expressways

Name: TURN_LANES_R
Code1: No intersection where a right turning movement is permitted exists on the section.
Code2: Turns permitted; multiple exclusive right turning lanes exist. Through movements are prohibited in these lanes. Multiple turning lanes allow for simultaneous turns from all turning lanes.
Code3: Turns permitted; a continuous exclusive right turning lane exists from intersection to intersection. Through movements are prohibited in this lane.
Code4: Turns permitted; a single exclusive right turning lane exists.
Code5: Turns permitted; no exclusive right turning lanes exist.
Code6: No right turns are permitted during the peak period.

Name: TURN_LANES_L
Code1: No intersection where a left turning movement is permitted exists on the section.
Code2: Turns permitted; multiple exclusive left turning lanes exist. Through movements are prohibited in these lanes. Multiple turning lanes allow for simultaneous turns from all turning lanes.
Code3: Turns permitted; a continuous exclusive left turning lane exists from intersection to intersection. Through movements are prohibited in this lane.
Code4: Turns permitted; a single exclusive left turning lane exists.
Code5: Turns permitted; no exclusive left turning lanes exist.
Code6: No left turns are permitted during the peak period.

Name: TOLL_CHARGED
Code1: Toll charged in one direction only.

Name: TOLL_TYPE
Code1: This section has toll lanes but no special tolls
Code3: This section has other special tolls.
